    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-07-31</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-10-27T20:43:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Combat Operations and Medical Benefit Authorization for Our Troops Act of 2008 or COMBAT Act - Increases the maximum monthly rates of: (1) hazardous duty pay; (2) hostile fire or imminent danger pay; (3) special pay for service as a member of a Weapons of Mass Destruction Civil Support Team; (4) special pay for members extending duty at designated overseas locations; (5) combat-related injury rehabilitation pay; and (6) the family separation allowance.</p> <p>Increases the maximum annual rates of special pay for: (1) officers serving as psychologists and nonphysician health care providers; and (2) special warfare officers extending their active-duty period.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>COMBAT Act</title>
