      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Display Title</titleType>
        <title>COMBAT Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 37, United States Code, to increase the maximum monthly rate for the military special pay known as hostile fire pay, imminent danger pay, or hazardous duty pay, to increase the maximum monthly rate for the family separation allowance paid to deployed members of the Armed Forces, and to increase other special and incentive pays to recognize the service of members of the Armed Forces and encourage recruitment and retention.</title>
      </item>
